OL,3,CCar knocks council worker over after
OL,4,Cignoring road closure signs
OL,6,FShocking footage shows the moment the
OL,7,Fdriver ran a council worker after
OL,8,Fdriving through a road closure
OL,10,FA driver has been sentenced after
OL,11,Freversing and running over a council
OL,12,Fworker on a road that was closed.
OL,14,FThis has prompted Derbyshire County
OL,15,FCouncil to appeal for respect towards
OL,16,Femployees after the roadworker was
OL,17,Fknocked over.
