OL,3,CCar knocks council worker over after
OL,4,Cignoring road closure signs
OL,6,FRoadworkers were fixing potholes on
OL,7,FLocko Lane, Hardstoft in May last year
OL,8,Fwhen dangerous driver John Leonard
OL,9,FMuckle drove past road closed signs
OL,10,Fand tried to get past a council truck
OL,11,Fon one side of the line.
OL,13,FMuckle couldn't do this and so
OL,14,Freversed in an attempt to go round the
OL,15,Fother side of the truck and in doing
OL,16,Fso knocked one of the workers into the
OL,17,Fhedgerow.
OL,19,FAfterwards, Muckle did not stop and
OL,20,Fdrove off. The roadworker involved was
OL,21,Fbadly bruised.
