OL,3,CCar knocks council worker over after
OL,4,Cignoring road closure signs
OL,6,FThe incident was reported to the
OL,7,Fpolice and the driver appeared at
OL,8,FDerby Crown Court last month.
OL,10,FMuckle pleaded guilty to dangerous
OL,11,Fdriving and was sentenced to eight
OL,12,Fmonths, suspended for twelve months
OL,13,Fand disqualified from driving for
OL,14,Ftwelve months.
OL,16,FDerbyshire County Council's Cabinet
OL,17,FMember for Highways Assets and
OL,18,FTransport, Councillor Charlotte Cupit,
OL,19,Fsaid: "Road closed signs are always
OL,20,Fthere for a very good reason.
